text:
Have stored with them for past more than 3 years. When I retrieved the box, the delivery guy expected me to pick 6 heavy box at lobby. Then when during delivery dropped my boxes twice on the street near my home. Few of the glass items broken.

When I call customer service then ask for the photos and said will investigate. After 4 days and 2 reminders, the answer was that I SHOULD HAVE NOT STORED FRAGILE in the box. Really????

I read the condition 4(d). Nothing mention about Fragile items.

Not even a apology from them. DO NOT STORE WITH THEM.
Saved me the hassle of bringing my stuff down. They pick up and deliver storage boxes.
This place offer you to storage your accessories......
